+Gem install docs \fIhttp://guides\.rubygems\.org/rubygems\-basics/#installing\-gems\fR
+.
+.IP "\(bu" 4
+Rubygems signing docs \fIhttp://guides\.rubygems\.org/security/\fR
+.
+.IP "" 0
